		"body": "<div style=\"margin-top:20px; display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap:27px; align-items:start;\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"body-lg\" style=\"margin:0;  font-size:20px;\">You now have the vocabulary, the mechanics, and the lens. Accounting is not arithmetic — it is a series of choices made visible.</p>\n\n        <div style=\"margin-top:13px; display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap:18px 28px; font-size:16px;\">\n          <div ><strong >Revenue timing</strong> — when did control transfer?</div>\n          <div ><strong >Depreciation method</strong> — which pattern fits the asset?</div>\n          <div ><strong >Inventory method</strong> — FIFO, LIFO, or weighted-average?</div>\n          <div ><strong >Impairment</strong> — is the carrying value still supported?</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"farsi-block\" style=\"margin-top:13px; font-size:18px; line-height:2.1;  \">\n          اکنون واژگان، مکانیک و نگاه لازم را در اختیار دارید. حسابداری صرفاً محاسبه نیست — مجموعه‌ای از انتخاب‌هاست که در قالب اعداد نمایان می‌شوند. هر رقم یک تصمیم است.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div >\n        <div style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.22em; color:var(--tan); text-transform:uppercase;\">Continue your refresh</div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:16px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px;\">\n          <div >\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Fraunces',serif; font-size:17px;  line-height:1.25;\">Read one real 10-K</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:16px;  margin-top:2px;\">Starbucks, Dutch Bros, or any company you buy from weekly.</div>\n          </div>\n          <div >\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Fraunces',serif; font-size:17px;  line-height:1.25;\">Practice 20 more problems</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:16px;  margin-top:2px;\">Weygandt, Kimmel &amp; Kieso (intermediate) is the standard.</div>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Fraunces',serif; font-size:17px;  line-height:1.25;\">Track one KPI for a quarter</div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:16px;  margin-top:2px;\">Free cash flow, or inventory days. Watch what moves the needle.</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-end;  \">\n      <div style=\"font-family:'Fraunces',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:19px; \">Welcome back to the profession.</div>\n      <div class=\"farsi\" style=\"font-size:19px; color:var(--tan); white-space:nowrap;\">به حرفه‌تان خوش برگشتید.</div>\n    </div>",
